{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239840/extras/first.gif?t=1731088817\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Merge Together is a relaxing two-player puzzle game where strategic thinking, harmony, and teamwork are key. Players aim to combine sweet fruits, level by level, to achieve larger fruits and ultimately reach the final goal: the watermelon.<br>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239840/extras/ezgif-4-f1d6a9e7eb.gif?t=1731088817\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">With simple and accessible mechanics, Merge Together enhances teamwork and communication through its two-player mode, creating a fun, competitive experience with friends.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239840/extras/ezgif-7-475eadf1ff.gif?t=1731088817\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Featuring colorful, delightful visuals and a soothing atmosphere, the game delivers a unique experience each time. As you progress, Merge Together offers both challenging puzzles and an enjoyable time. Its smooth gameplay makes each move exciting, keeping the joy of the game alive.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239840/extras/ezgif-4-db32c75b10.gif?t=1731088817\" /></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Watermelon","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3239840/af8929b8b0c504d1096587f7a5113353f2494d3c.jpg"},{"name":"500","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3239840/4684ce8df772978ff0943c22cc43ee68402e56c5.jpg"},{"name":"250","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3239840/26a30e480677d449835b840872dff6e7fdc3fe48.jpg"},{"name":"1500","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic